&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate combines strong operational leadership with deep infrastructure expertise and a proven track record leading cloud adoption, infrastructure modernization, and technology transformation initiatives. This director will work closely with the CTO to develop and execute a long-term technology strategy that supports both our business objectives and the future evolution of our technology ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
