&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our rockstar team at 1-800 Contacts!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to make a difference in an industry that’s all about empowering people to see clearly? At SeekWell (parent company of 1-800 Contacts, The Framery and Luna), we’re always on the lookout for passionate, innovative individuals who thrive helping others and want to be part of a company that truly puts the customer first.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are currently not hiring&lt;/strong&gt; but are &lt;em&gt;continuously&lt;/em&gt; accepting resumes for our Customer Department. If you think you’re a great fit, submit your application!&lt;/p&gt;
