&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who we are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At SeekWell, our goal is simple: make it easier for people to access the vision care they need. For almost 30 years, 1-800 Contacts has led the charge with legendary, award-winning service, and we’re continuing that legacy through innovation, top-notch products, and businesses that make customers cheer.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re proud to be backed by KKR, one of the world’s largest private equity firms, but it’s our people who make us great.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why you&#39;ll love us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For over 30 years, 1-800 Contacts has excelled in simplifying the process of getting contact lenses, while making it affordable and hassle-free. AND, we empower our team to make it happen—without jumping through hoops or asking for permission. Our employees rave about our culture, our commitment to customer satisfaction, and how every day brings a new opportunity to WOW someone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t your average call center job; it’s a career where you can thrive, grow, and be part of a winning team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sound like you? Apply now, and let&#39;s see if we’re a perfect fit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
