&lt;li&gt;Growth mindset demonstrated through continuous learning, embracing challenges, and developing new technical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to deliver well-defined projects and tasks with appropriate guidance and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work and communicate effectively in a collaborative technology team environment&lt;/li&gt;
